title: Total.War.ROME.II.Update.13_1.Hotfix.and.Festivals.Update + Asse
description:
This version contains everything released from CA up to Update.13_1.Hotfix.and.Festivals.Update build: 11724.548874 plus the assembly kit plus the mod manager ( u can delete it if u dont use it), all u have to do to run the kit is:
1) Extract all files to your Rome 2 <root> install dir
2) Start with /binaries/BOB.AssemblyKit.exe & TWeak.AssemblyKit.exe
3) Enjoy
